&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Medha Patkar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;An Indian &lt;strong&gt;social activist and former Politician &lt;/strong&gt;working on various &lt;strong&gt;crucial political and economic issues raised by tribals, Dalits, farmers, laborers, and women facing injustice in India.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
